Keyword who~
Level 0
Text
Name       : who
Synopsis   : who -f|-n|-e|-h
Description:

This command shows you all users online with various items of
information such as their partial IP address, how long they are
online, and their titles.  * sign in front of the ip address
column means, that user is toggled his/her message express, and
you cannot send X messages to that user if you are not in that
user's friend list.  This list is sorted according to the users'
online time.

    who -f          Lists online users that are in your frield list.
    who -n          Lists online users that are in your enemy list.
    who -e          Lists online users that are in your notify list.
    who -h          This help.
~
End
