a user while being eXpress disabled, just put his/her name into this list.
Optional part lets you write a comment upto 60 characters about the user.  You
can use -r to remove a user from your friend list.  Maximum number of friends
that you can put into your list is 50.  -f option is used to completely delete
your friend list.

Examples: friend deneme example (puts user Deneme into your friend list)
          friend -r deneme      (removes user Deneme from your friend list)
          friend -f             (completely deletes your friend list)
          friend                (prints your friends to the screen)
~
End
